<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200918/b28ba32e73e2405da749952c0b6bf50b.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图3：一键应用“美白”画面风格</span></img></p>
